third
quarter
of
this
year
.
###
Health-care
companies
should
get
healthier
in
the
third
quarter
.
###
Medical-supply
houses
are
expected
to
report
earnings
increases
of
about
15
%
on
average
for
the
third
quarter
,
despite
sales
