in
all
of
the
company
's
markets
.
###
Net
income
rose
to
$
699
million
,
or
65
cents
a
share
,
from
the
year-earlier
$
587
million
or
55
cents
a
share
.
###
Revenue
edged
up
to
$
8.9
billion
from
$
8.81
billion
.
###
The
latest
period
's
net
was
reduced
$
102
million
,
or
nine
cents
a
share
,
for
a
