machine
of
the
1990s
.
###
Appealing
to
a
young
audience
,
he
scraps
an
old
reference
to
Ozzie
and
Harriet
and
instead
quotes
the
Grateful
Dead
.
###
The
lyric
chosen
--
``
long
strange
night
''
--
may
be
an
apt
footnote
to
television
spots
by
both
candidates
intended
to
portray
