.
###
He
is
n't
sure
a
recession
is
coming
,
but
says
the
other
likely
alternative
--
reignited
inflation
--
is
just
as
bad
.
###
``
This
late
in
an
expansion
,
''
the
economy
tends
to
veer
off
either
into
damaging
inflation
or
into
a
recession
,
Mr.
Confair
says
.
###
The
Federal
Reserve
Board
's
plan
for
a
``
soft
landing
,
''
he
says
,
requires
the
Fed
to
navigate
``
an
ever-narrowing
corridor
.
''
###
A
soft
landing
is
n't
something
that
can
be
achieved
once
and
